title: Railworks TS2015 Los Angeles Commuter Rail F59PH
description:
The Los Angeles Commuter Rail F59PH for Train Simulator features cab and instrument lighting, Control Cab Car and passenger cars. 

The locomotive is also Quick Drive compatible, giving you the freedom to drive the Los Angeles Commuter Rail F59PH on any Quick Drive enabled route for Train Simulator. Also included are scenarios specifically for the Pacific SurflinerÃ‚Â®: LA-San Diego route (available separately and required to play these scenarios).
